<pre style="font-family: Georgia;">{{lead.First Name:default=Hi}},<br /> <br />On behalf of Perrier-Jou&euml;t, thank you for coming to the opening of the Soho 189 Art Lane / 2014-15 Sovereign Asian Art Prize Finalists&rsquo; Exhibition during Hong Kong Art Week.<br /> <br />I hope you enjoyed the party and our Perrier-Jou&euml;t champagne, and would like to take a few minutes of your time to follow up on the below:</pre>
